      "writtenOn": "2020-07-08T08:06:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In this CL, logs from croslog are referred in two names: \"combined logs\" and \"system logs\". I want them to be aligned for clarity.\n\nIMHO \"system logs\" is a bit confusing because it\u0027s not the only logs in the CrOS system (at this moment). I recommend deciding a unique name and using it consistently throughout your project.\n\nSome possible recommendations:\n\n- Unified logs\n- Combined logs\n- Collective logs\n\nc.f. https://www.thesaurus.com/browse/unified",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 45,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 45,
        "endChar": 19
      },
